# Database Design: AI-Powered Appraisal System

## Database Type Selection

| Decision | Selection | Justification |
|----------|-----------|----------------|
| **Primary Database** | PostgreSQL 16+ | ACID compliance, JSONB support for flexible metrics, full-text search, strong indexing |
| **Caching Layer** | Redis 7.x | Session storage, rate limiting, real-time sync queues |
| **Time-Series** | TimescaleDB (PostgreSQL extension) | Performance trend data, metric history |
| **Search** | PostgreSQL Full-Text Search | Employee search, audit log search |

**Rationale for PostgreSQL:**
- Strong data integrity for appraisal/HR data
- JSONB columns for flexible integration data (Jira, Git payloads)
- Row-level security for multi-tenant/role isolation
- Audit logging with triggers
- Excellent full-text search capabilities

## Entity List

