| `appraisal_cycles` | Review periods (H1 2026, H2 2026) | Manager, HR, Admin |
| `appraisals` | Manager-finalized appraisals | Manager, HR, Employee |
| `ai_drafts` | AI-generated draft appraisals | Manager |
| `metrics_aggregated` | Pre-computed performance metrics | Employee, Manager |
